OL,5, A school attacked over its toilet      
OL,6, policy has revealed staff have been    
OL,7, abused and threatened with violence.   
OL,9,FCrowds gathered outside The Farnley    
OL,10,FAcademy on Monday to protest after a   
OL,11,FTikTok-influenced trend encouraged     
OL,12,Fchildren to vent against school rules. 
OL,14,FOutside the gates, pupils chanted "let 
OL,15,Fus wee" in response to claims students 
OL,16,Fwere subject to strict loo rules.      
OL,18,FIn a letter, head Chris Stokes said    
OL,19,Fthreats to staff would not be          
OL,20,Ftolerated.                             
